data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This remarkable property offers a fantastic combination of comfort, space, and functionality. With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a bonus room, it's perfect for your needs.  Inside, the spacious living room is ideal for entertaining or relaxing with loved ones. The well-appointed kitchen boasts modern appliances and ample storage space. There's also a versatile bonus room, perfect for a home office or guest bedroom.  Car enthusiasts and hobbyists will appreciate the garage and large barn/workshop, providing plenty of storage and creative space. Outside, the landscaped yard offers a serene and peaceful retreat.  Experience country living at its best with this property.
